data.title: OST: Dad's Army - Music from the Television Series
data.meta_description: This popular 72 minute, 26 track CD album features original music from the classic BBC comedy series Dad's Army, including the immortal theme song performed by Bud Flanagan as well as popular songs from the 1930s and 1940s. All tracks have been carefully remastered using modern digital technology. The CD runs for 75 mi
